 :description
 "kotoba-Datomic-native STRUCTURAL atlas of every government unit on Earth — supranational → country → region/subdivision → prefecture → municipality/ward → ministry (省) → agency (庁) → bureau (局) → division (課) → section → 窓口 (madoguchi) — each carrying 住所 (address) / 窓口 (service window) / 書式 (form) / 手続き (procedure) / langgraph-Pregel EDN procedure graph; BPMN is optional visual/legacy interop. Ministry-level rows carry :gov.unit/cofog, using COFOG as the international government-function numbering layer. Functional coverage is computed in CLJC from suffix + COFOG + conservative multi-portfolio signals, so merged ministries count toward every explicit function they carry. It is the member-support SSoT that danjo (watches the state), kanae (fiscal-flow viz), tsumugi (power-graph), toritsugi (citizen procedure concierge) and himotoki (disclosure) all consume for the 'who / where / how' of public administration — so they stop re-deriving it ad hoc. CONSTITUTIONAL POSTURE: a member-authorized administrative support agent + civic operations map, exactly like tsumugi ('accountability map, NEVER a target-list') and watatsuna ('resilience map, NEVER a target-list'). Per-unit atlas DIDs (did:web:etzhayyim.com:gov:<iso3>:...) identify ooyake's SUPPORT-AGENT RECORD for a real public body — they NEVER claim to BE the government, NEVER are an official channel, NEVER issue/accept anything on a government's behalf (§2(c) impersonation ban, G3). ooyake supports etzhayyim members with guidance, drafting, preparation, tracking, and handoff; external submission, payment, signature, or government-record mutation requires explicit member consent, applicable legal/licensed boundary checks, and an audit trail. It never audits/adjudicates (→ danjo). Public-data-only (G4), non-fabrication with provenance + last-verified + :authoritative/:representative sourcing (G5), no personal data of officials (G6), Murakumo-only (G7), non-commercial (G8), member-authorized support (G9), civic-wayfinding-never-target-list (G10), politically neutral (G11), freshness-gated (G12). JP-first proof-of-model (R0); architecture jurisdiction-generic. Amends ADR-2605242330 §2 (per-unit enumeration admitted as a bounded member-support atlas, NOT routing-around). 10 cells / 8 Lexicons / 12 gates / 11 non-goals.",
 :description-ja
 "全世界の政府単位を網羅する kotoba-Datomic-native の構造アトラス — 超国家 → 国 → 広域/地方 → 都道府県 → 市区町村 → 省 → 庁 → 局 → 課 → 係 → 窓口 まで。各単位が 住所 / 窓口 / 書式 / 手続き / langgraph-Pregel EDN の手続きグラフを保持し、BPMN は任意の可視化/legacy interop として扱う。省庁単位には国際的な政府機能分類番号として COFOG を :gov.unit/cofog に持たせる。機能 coverage は suffix + COFOG + 複合省庁名の保守的 signal から CLJC で算出し、統合省庁が持つ複数機能を coverage に反映する。danjo(国家を監視)・kanae(財政フロー可視化)・tsumugi(権力グラフ)・toritsugi(市民手続きコンシェルジュ)・himotoki(開示)が公共行政の『誰が/どこで/どうやって』を引くための member-support の SSoT(各 actor が個別に再構築しなくて済む)。憲法的姿勢: member の行政手続き・行政活動を支援する agent + civic operations map。単位ごとの atlas DID(did:web:etzhayyim.com:gov:<iso3>:...)は実在の公的機関に対する ooyake の支援 agent 記録を指すのであって、政府そのものを名乗らない・公式 channel ではない・政府の代わりに何かを発行/受理しない(§2(c) なりすまし禁止、G3)。ooyake は etzhayyim member の行政手続き・行政活動について、案内・下書き・準備・追跡・handoff を支援する agent。外部提出・支払・署名・政府記録変更は member の明示承認、適用される法務/資格境界、監査 trail を必須とする。監査/裁定はしない(→ danjo)。公開データのみ(G4)、provenance + last-verified + :authoritative/:representative sourcing による非捏造(G5)、職員個人情報の不保持(G6)、Murakumo-only(G7)、非営利(G8)、member-authorized support (G9)、市民導線であって標的リストにしない(G10)、政治的中立(G11)、freshness-gated(G12)。日本先行の proof-of-model(R0);architecture は jurisdiction 汎用。ADR-2605242330 §2 を改正(単位列挙を『routing-around ではなく member-support アトラス』として限定的に許容)。10 cells / 8 Lexicons / 12 gates / 11 non-goals。",
